result.reason: Issue title only — no description, steps, or CSV sample provided; unclear if this is a bug (import fails when SQL backend is active) or a feature request (CSV import not supported for SQL storage).
result.approach: Await clarification: if CSV import silently drops connections when SQL backend is selected, wire CsvConnectionsDeserializer through the SQL save path; if feature request, add a dedicated Import→CSV menu item that loads via CsvConnectionsDeserializer and persists through the active IConnectionsService backend
